Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海和凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为魔法骑士，她们需要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由传说矿物\N艾斯古托造成的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，为了得到那些武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人付出了很大的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人失去了创师普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍身的菲力欧 沙漠之恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风，那不是菲力欧所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会实现愿望的宝石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样，想到愿望了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，还没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吧，那种事要立即试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你试试 借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的剑击大赛难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个来到锡菲罗时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一星期后举行的比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海，我们来到锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,己过了一个多星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗是意志的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祈求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间也会过得慢点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得小海\N认为真的会那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，小光你也许个愿看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会聋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 闪光是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你的哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光是我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到小风了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗又开始崩溃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不服气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还未成为魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要令魔神苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫我有很多事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也想问关于魔神的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但古列夫你平安吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变成…石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样仍能和你们的心对话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不如尽快拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿知道魔神的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照莫歌拿的指示前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们真的会成为魔法骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果又是无聊话，我会生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望菲力欧平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只管说无聊话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔法骑士在兴高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把可爱的亚杜兰提杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴杰罗，你轻易就能打倒她们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，怎样引她们出来好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只魔物看来很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫菲力欧，是个流浪艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能控制这种魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是谢加图大人\N直属的召唤士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个仰慕谢加图大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把那些\N魔法骑士引诱出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，请您饶命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说谎，你怎会做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您试试我是否做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了对大人您也没损失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您向谢加图大人引荐我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图会见你这种家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，请大人您收我为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只会饶你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢大人，我竟然能成为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人您这种召唤士的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，我立即去办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要护照之类的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么也有吧，莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村看来很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位好，我们又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里遇上也是某种缘份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请客，如何?来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害羞别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要几位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是敝店自豪的糕点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘，告诉她们那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林后面突然出现了一片沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没人目睹过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说那里住有可怕的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然没人见过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为何知道它很可怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去过的人没有再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个沙漠出现后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和城市的联系中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日常用品没有再运来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，几位慢用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事\N你们打算置之不理吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧，小海，小风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吗?我还未享受糕点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要帮助有麻烦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义大前提下\N糕点要暂放一旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带路就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你，菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好记着她们的声音，巴杰罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是那个沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿你在这里等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是大人您的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点事易如反掌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得您赞赏我好光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑收你为徒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你看来很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我和你们无仇无怨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我需要你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心\N我会救出艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂暴停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是巴杰罗的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，我们去参观\N魔法骑士的死期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等阿斯克特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您也带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跌下去我也不会埋你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害的魔物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使怎样厉害的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有一两处弱点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它只能在沙漠活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有它只能凭声音捕捉猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怪物对声音有反应，不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴杰罗 不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沙漠上赢不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什么原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧在沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾和我们并肩作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有要骗我们的理由呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风你也那样想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧的行动太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想救他，你们就来沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若明天前不来\N我会杀死菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能又是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚才菲力欧的\N声音救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光说的话可能没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不同意立即出发救人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日找不到办法打倒那魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前去沙漠就等于送死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但菲力欧他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人去救菲力欧和锡菲罗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有时间，我们慢慢想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时，我没发觉他拼命在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何能听到我们的声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光，光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行小风不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，小风也真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大声也不醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我做饵引魔法骑士出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说负担太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你为何要救她们?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一时冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想试试巴杰罗的力量罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧 看啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴杰罗，之后拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要来?我骗过你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我想到被你骗了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常伤心，觉得不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次被人骂我是傻瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正谈得投契，这怪物真不通气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风，你有带着那东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你的那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧，那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我引开它的注意，你趁机走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能快点回去东京…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能胜出剑击大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望菲力欧平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑成长了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过去这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为武器成长了才没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你有点反常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点反常的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明骗了我们 却又救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伴到了 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是实现愿望的宝石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法通话器，能传达说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要我帮忙，随时叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也要看我高兴才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会对付小光和小海 再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风你瞒着我们自己偷偷来太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…你的剑…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何胡来后小风的武器会成长了啊 不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讲理 乱来都可以成长的话 偷窥狂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横冲直撞的司机 大家都会成为魔法骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信 真是的 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕基罗 竟敢对我的朋友做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可饶恕 魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士…

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
